attributes.title: THE. WORST.APP
attributes.review: I just want to start off that I opened the app to a picture of a Cheeto colored man that had the pointiest hair. It was so unpleasant to see the picture of this Cheeto man that I nearly fainted. Luckily, my phone saved me and died because it couldn’t handle the stupidity of the picture, that my phone displayed. SOMEHOW my fingers took over and with no control, I wrote a review and starred the lowest possible choice. and I’m definitely deleting this app. But unfortunately I can’t get that disturbing picture of the president Cheeto out of my mind😪
